window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>USA Today and Wall Street Journa</i>l best-selling author Tracy Lorraine brings you a new dark mafia high school romance story set in the Knight's Ridge Empire world.</p> <p><b>Roses are red.</b></p> <p><b>Violets are blue.</b></p> <p>I'm hot, and I need you.</p> <p>I'll be in room 69 waiting on the bed.</p> <p>I hope you're in the mood for giving h....</p> <p>If you're up for a game.</p> <p>I promise to scream your name.</p> <p><i>Corrupt Valentine's Knight </i>is a prequel to the Corrupt trilogy. If you like mafia bad boys who like to be in control and strong heroines who know what they want, then this is for you!</p>"; 
